name: minnesota-school-district-and-attendance-boundaries-school-year-2004-2005
notes: This file represents the boundaries of all public school districts and school attendance areas in the state of Minnesota for school year 2004-2005. Each year Minnesota school districts identify their current elementary, middle and high school attendance area boundaries. This district attendance file is maintained at LMIC but is also supplied to the State of Minnesota Legislative Coordinating Commission. The LCC keeps the 'official' school distirct information for the State of Minnesota.
